cs.CV, cs.LG, cs.RO, cs.AI, cs.MM 

This paper deals with computer vision and machine learning techniques to predict 3D poses of people from video sequences. Therefore, the most likely category is cs.CV (Computer Vision and Pattern Recognition). The paper also involves regression techniques, which falls under the category of cs.LG (Machine Learning). The use of motion information and linking frames suggests the involvement of robotics and control, which falls under the category of cs.RO (Robotics). The paper also involves the use of deep learning techniques, which falls under the category of cs.AI (Artificial Intelligence). Finally, the paper involves the use of video sequences, which falls under the category of cs.MM (Multimedia).
